project_descr: This project facilitates the audit of the Support to Suriname Elections 2010 project

outputs.output_descr: This project is a continuation of the "Support to Suriname Elections 2010" project which was implemented using DEX modality. The latter project was operationally closed, since the DEX approval was nearing expiry date and activities as such had been concluded. The Support to Suriname Elections 2010 project included a post electoral component which aimed at assisting the country to evaluate/assess previous elections, and design a way forward. Under this new project, the mandatory DEX/DIM audit will be done.
